room_title: Escape room "Revenge on the Bayou" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: We had a blast tonight in the swamp room with our group of 7. We were so close!! Will definitely be back to try another room.

room_title: Escape room "Revenge on the Bayou" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: My friends and I had a blast trying to escape the haunted swamp room! Will definitely be going again. I would recommend this to anybody that enjoys a challenging puzzle. A must go.

room_title: Escape room "Revenge on the Bayou" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: We had an absolute blast in the Haunted Swamp Room!!!! We were so close to making our escape! We can't wait to come back and try a different room!

room_title: Escape room "Revenge on the Bayou" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: We did this as a team building exercise. When I first heard that we were going to be locked In a room we had to escape from I was like...what?!?Let me just say that we had the absolute best time. Everyone should get some friends together and do this! It was a very unique experience.
